<h2>How Can I Get Help with Delivery?</h2>
<p>Shipments go out every Friday, with delivery to your school typically on Mondays or Tuesdays.</p>
<p>Shipments are addressed to the School Librarian, with the requesting teacher’s name in the accompanying binder. Teacher Sets arrive in bright red bins or yellow padded envelopes. All shipments contain prepaid UPS labels for return delivery.</p>
<p>When ordering available Teacher Sets, allow 2 weeks for delivery.</p>
<p>Delivery Questions? Email <a href="mailto:delivery@mylibrarynyc.org">delivery@mylibrarynyc.org</a> to request additional bins, mailing envelopes, postage paid labels, or for help with delivery-related questions.</p>
